 809 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/allah-gives-no-weight\/","url_meta":{"origin":3984,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fame: Allah gives no weight to worldly status","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, a prominent and obese man will be brought on the Day of Resurrection who does not weigh as much as a gnat's wing to Allah. Recite the verse: Thus, We will not give them any\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/03\/surat-al-kahf-friday-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":3984,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Kahf: Reading Surat al-Kahf on Friday brings light","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites Surat al-Kahf on Friday, a light will shine for him between this Friday and the next.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5996 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35164,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/07\/beautiful-recitation\/","url_meta":{"origin":3984,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qira\u2019ah: The Prophet beautifies his recitation of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: I heard the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, reciting in the evening prayer, \u201cBy the fig and the olive,\u201d (95:1). I have not heard a voice more beautiful than his. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 769, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 464 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14036,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/07\/ibn-masud-quran-old-treasures\/","url_meta":{"origin":3984,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Quran: Middle chapters are my old treasures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Yazid reported: Ibn Mas\u2